Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.65,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hide a scarlet letter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.40,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Manuals in hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.49,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We paint the world a bit redder
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:18.53,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bury my new friend, means to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.87,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Decomposing sailor shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:23.12,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Button down jackets, pleated skirts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.87,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.59,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In the mirror I am cinderella
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.67,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Too late to reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:38.47,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If the future needs a billion samples of flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.68,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I’m your reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.93,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I’ve no colour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:47.86,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So the least I can do for you is endure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:51.98,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We walked down the aisle unexplored
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:56.78,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We walked down the aisle unexplored
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.37,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Remaining strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.91,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Laykarf dunon a hethkka ja
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.04,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dullun katre n’a sol solle flare-esta
